extends layout

block content
  section.features
    .hero
      .content.black-banner
        h1 Cloud-managed Wi-Fi for Everyone.
        h2
          | Cucumber Tony, our magnificent cloud-based portal, gives you everything you need to manage your Wi-Fi networks.
          br
          | From branded login pages and email capture to advanced networking tools and retail analytics.
        br
        .next(data-next="main")
          a(href="#", class="btn btn-large btn-success") READ MORE
  hr#main
  .container
    section
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          h1 Create Wi-Fi Networks Anysize, Anywhere.
          h3 Cucumber Tony makes it really simple to get started. Adding a box takes seconds and you'll see it online in under 60 seconds.
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-center
            p Create new Wi-Fi locations and manage them from one dashboard. You'll be able to see all your boxes on a single page, from anywhere in the world.
            p
              | And, when you need to make a change, you do it all from Cucumber Tony. Changes are&nbsp;
              b sent within seconds.&nbsp;
              | Update hundreds of boxes with a single click.
            p
              | There's lots of different boxes (routers) to choose from too. Either buy one from the&nbsp;
              a(href='/shop') shop&nbsp;
              | (you'll need to sign-in to your CT account). Or, you can download and install the firmware on one of the&nbsp;
              a(href="opensource-wifi-firmware") compatible devices here.&nbsp;
            p Get cracking and sign-up for Cucumber Tony now, it's free to start.
            p
              a(href="/signup", class="btn btn-large btn-default") SIGN-UP

          .hidden-xs.hidden-sm.col-md-6.text-center
            img(src="/images/wifi-features/wifi-hotspot-map.png", class='img img-responsive img-centre')

    hr
    section
     .row
       .col-xs-12
         h1 Design Beautiful Login Pages
         h3 If you want to offer public Wi-Fi, you'll want a nice looking login page. These are the gatekeeper to your Internet connection.
     .row
       .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-left
          p Pick a layout template add your own images and text. All login pages are responsive, in fact they might even look better on a mobile.
          p Already got hardware? No worries, you can use the captive portal with other devices including Ruckus, Aruba, Xirrus, Cisco Meraki and OpenMesh.
          p
            | Read more about the&nbsp;
            a(href="/captive-portal") captive portal here

          p
            a(href="/signup", class="btn btn-large btn-default") SIGN-UP
        .hidden-xs.hidden-sm.col-md-6.text-center
          img(src="/images/wifi-features/iphone-wifi-login.png", class='img img-responsive img-centre')

    hr
    section
     .row
      .col-xs-12
         h1 Authorise Guests and Capture Emails.
         h3 Automatically add emails to your MailChimp and Campaign Monitor accounts.
     .row
      .col-xs-12
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-left
          p
            | Add your&nbsp;
            b MailChimp&nbsp;
            | or&nbsp;
            b Campaign Montor&nbsp;
            | list IDs and activate the newsletter and an email field will automatically appear on your login screens. After a customer signs-in, their email will appear in your list.
          p Then you can send them nice emails with special offers and stuff.

          p
            a(href="/signup", class="btn btn-large btn-default") SIGN-UP
        .hidden-xs.hidden-sm.col-md-6.text-center

           img(src="/images/wifi-features/authorise-guest-wifi.png", class='img img-responsive img-centre')

    hr
    section
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          h1 Monitor & Manage Every Access Point
          h3 Monitor every Wi-Fi access point in your network remotely. Cucumber Tony has the only real time Wi-Fi activity feed out there, making it even easier to diagnose and fix faults.
          img(src="/images/wifi-features/wifi-analytics-graph-2.png", class='img img-responsive img-centre')

    hr
    section
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          h1 Public &amp; Private Networks
          br
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-left
            p
              b Not just for businesses!&nbsp;
              | Lots of people use CT in their homes and offices too.

            p
              | Cucumber Tony lets you create multiple networks quickly and easily. One for private use one for your applications like your tills and sound system and one for guest to access. So you'll always be seperate from your guests.

            p You can hide the networks too if you don't need them. And each network has it's own rules so you can give priority to your private one (if you want).

            p
              a(href="/signup", class="btn btn-large btn-default") SIGN-UP

          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-center
            img(src="/images/wifi-features/more-wifi-features/public-private-networks.png", class='img img-responsive img-centre')

    hr
    section
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          h1 Get to Know Your Visitors
          h3 Understand who's using your Wi-Fi without getting creepy. You're not a stalker are you, we hope not.
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-left
            p What do you know about the people who visit, or even why they visit.
            p Cucumber Tony gets you nice and familiar with your audience by mapping visitor demographics and venue performance. The more you know, the easier it is to keep everyone happy.

            a(href="/signup", class="btn btn-large btn-default") SIGN-UP
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.text-center
            img(src="/images/wifi-features/boys-and-girls.png", class='img img-responsive img-centre')

    include more-features-footer
